details.name: Battle Hunger
details.description: Enrages an enemy unit, causing it to be slowed and take damage over time until it kills another unit or the duration ends. Axe gains movement speed for each unit affected with Battle Hunger. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Battle Hunger provides -30% damage output reduction. Applies Battle Hunger on nearby enemies after a successful Culling Blade.
